outputs.output_descr: The Emprendedores y Tecnologia (Empretec) is a unique UNCTAD programme that provides entrepreneurial training to owners of Small and Medium Enterprises (SMEs). Its current implementation in Jordan  is the result of close cooperation among UNCTAD as principal partner and originator, the United Nations Development Programme in Jordan (UNDP-Jordan), the Ministry of Planning and International Cooperation (MOPIC) of the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan, and the Jordan Loan Guarantee Cooperation (JLGC) which is also the national counterpart.

project_title: empretec programme in jordan phase iii
